section.book-a-table
    .book-a-table__wrapper
        h2.book-a-table.title.playfair-bold.fz35.color_dark
            | Book a table
        p.book-a-table.description.sintony-normal.fz14.color_lighter-gray
            | Lorem Ipsum has been the industry's standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book.
            .book-a-table__form-part
                form.fz14.sintony-normal.color_less-dark(action="submit")
                    span.column
                        .inner-column-wrap
                            img.inner-column__icon(src="./images/reserve-form/name.png", alt="name")
                            input.inner-column(type="text" placeholder="Name*")
                        .inner-column-wrap
                            img.inner-column__icon(src="./images/reserve-form/date.png", alt="name")
                            input.inner-column(type="text" placeholder="Date*")
                    span.column
                        .inner-column-wrap
                            img.inner-column__icon(src="./images/reserve-form/email.png", alt="name")
                            input.inner-column(type="email" placeholder="Email*")
                        .inner-column-wrap
                            img.inner-column__icon(src="./images/reserve-form/time.png", alt="name")
                            input.inner-column(type="text" placeholder="Time*")
                    span.column
                        .inner-column-wrap
                            img.inner-column__icon(src="./images/reserve-form/phone.png", alt="name")
                            input.inner-column(type="tel" placeholder="Phone*")
                        .inner-column-wrap
                            img.inner-column__icon(src="./images/reserve-form/guest.png", alt="name")
                            input.inner-column(type="text" placeholder="Guests*")
                    .inner-column-wrap.textarea-block
                        img.inner-column__textarea-icon(src="./images/reserve-form/comment.png", alt="name")
                        textarea.reqs.fz14.sintony-normal.color_less-dark(type="text" placeholder= "Special Requirements*")
                        button.btn.reqs-btn(href='#') Make Reservation